APPENDICE A - QUICK REFERENCE ENCODING
=============================================================================
HEADER (12 byte, packed):
  magic u16 (0x5342 LE); verType u8 ([7:4]Ver=1 [3:0]MsgType);
  flags u8; srcNodeId u16 LE; dstNodeId u16 LE (0xFFFF bcast);
  sequence u16 LE; typeHop u8 ([7:4]NodeType [3:0]HopLimit);
  payloadLen u8 (0-241).
FLAGS: 0x01 ACK_REQUIRED 0x02 ACK 0x04 ENCRYPTED 0x08 FRAGMENTED
       0x10 ROUTED 0x20 RAW  0x40 (PRIORITY futuro)/0x80 riservati(=0)
NODETYPE: 0 Generic 1 Sensor 2 Gateway 3 Relay 4 Actuator 5 Experimental
MSGTYPE: 1 TELEMETRY 2 EVENT 3 COMMAND 4 RESPONSE 5 ACK 6 HEARTBEAT
PAYLOAD: FLAG_RAW=0 -> TLV; FLAG_RAW=1 -> PayloadLen byte opachi.
CLASS A: [TYPE 1B (0-127)][LEN 1B][VALUE]
CLASS B: [TYPE 2B: B0=0x80|(ID>>8), B1=ID&0xFF][LEN 1B][VALUE]
Profile: [0x32][LEN][ProfId][Data]
CRC: CRC16-CCITT-FALSE(Header+Payload), 2B LE.
payload_len = frame_len - 14 (EXPLICIT: PayloadLen = quel valore in TX,
verifica facoltativa in RX; IMPLICIT: PayloadLen autoritativo).
ACCESSO CANALE: CAD/LBT + backoff + jitter +/-15%.
DUTY CYCLE: t_off = ToA/dc - ToA (1% o 10% secondo sotto-banda). NORMATIVO.
PHY: BW 62.5 kHz, CR 4/8, explicit, CRC PHY on; LDRO a SF>=10.
Payload max: 241 byte. Allineato a MeshCore EU/UK Narrow (SF8).
SECURITY (15.7): Livello 0 in v0.1 (Unsecured); Livello 1 AEAD AES-128-GCM
con nonce a 96 bit = NodeId(16)||ExtCounter(32)||Epoch(48); Livello 2 Key
Model Auth in versione futura.
